query: SELECT c.slug, c.name, COUNT(pc.photoId) as photo_count FROM collaborators c LEFT JOIN photo_collaborators pc ON c.id = pc.collaboratorId WHERE c.isVisible = 1 GROUP BY c.id HAVING photo_count > 0 LIMIT 1;
